Usage
-----
Create your flake8 file as usual:

.. code:: shell-session

    $ flake8 --output-file flake8.txt

Convert it to JUnit format:

.. code:: shell-session

    $ flake8_junit flake8.txt flake8_junit.xml

Running the tests
-----------------

.. code:: shell-session

    $ pip install -r requirements_dev.txt
    $ tox


